==Arabic==
===Etymology===
From Arabic {{ARchar|[[جهد]]}} (jáhada), to endeavor, to strive, to labor.

===Noun===
'''{{ARchar|جهاد}}''' (jihād) {{m}}

#[[fight]], [[battle]]
#[[jihad]], [[holy war]] ''(against the infidels)''

